{"title_page": "Vol. 2 Tour", "text_new": "{{Infobox concert\n|album=''[[Formula, Vol. 2]]''\n|artist=[[Romeo Santos]]\n|concert_tour_name=Formula, Vol. 2 Tour\n|start_date=March 7, 2014\n|end_date=August 27, 2016\n|image=\n|number_of_legs=3\n|number_of_shows=53 in North America<br />41 in Latin America<br />18 in Europe<br />112 played\n|last_tour=[[The King Stays King]] (2012-2013)\n|next_tour=[[Golden Tour (Romeo Santos tour)|Golden Tour]] (2018-2019)\n}}\n\n'''Formula, Vol. 2 Tour''' was a concert tour by the Domininican American singer [[Romeo Santos]], to promote his album [[Formula, Vol. 2]]. This concert tour was a commercial success, selling out arenas and stadiums all over America and Europe, including [[Yankee Stadium]] in New York.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/latin/6545738/romeo-santos-billboard-cover-sexuality-fatherhood-crossover-success|title=Billboard Cover: Romeo Santos on Selling Out Stadiums 'Like Beyonce,' Rumors About His Sexuality and Manning Up as a Father|website=Billboard|access-date=2019-05-04}}</ref>\n\n== Tour dates ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:175px;\" |Date\n! style=\"width:150px;\" |City\n! style=\"width:150px;\" |Country\n! style=\"width:250px;\" |Venue\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |North America\n|-\n|March 7, 2014\n|Monterrey\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Mexico\n|Arena Monterrey\n|-\n|March 8, 2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Mexico City\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Mexico City Arena\n|-\n|March 9, 2014\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |Europe\n|-\n|March 18, 2014\n|Olivia\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Spain\n|Recinto Ferial De Corralejo\n|-\n|March 21, 2014\n|Madrid\n|Plaza de Toros de Las Ventas\n|-\n|March 22, 2014\n|Bacerlona\n|Palau Sant Jordi\n|-\n|March 23, 2014\n|Paris\n|France \n|Zenith de Paris\n|-\n|March 26, 2014\n|Milan\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Italy\n|Mediolanum Forum\n|-\n|March 27, 2014\n|Rome\n|Palalottomatica\n|-\n|March 30, 2014\n|London\n|United Kingdown\n|O2 Academy Brixton\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |South America<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eonline.com/ar/news/597971/romeo-santos-confirma-su-gran-momento-con-un-recital-en-el-estadio-de-river-plate|title=Romeo Santos confirma su gran momento con un recital en el Estadio de River Plate|date=2014-11-14|website=E! Online|language=es-AR|accessdate=2019-05-04}}</ref>\n|-\n|April 5, 2014\n|Buenos Aires\n|Argentina\n|Estadio GEBA\n|-\n|April 29, 2014\n|Santiago\n|Chile\n|Movistar Arena\n|-\n|May 3, 2014\n| rowspan=\"5\" |Buenos Aires\n| rowspan=\"5\" |Argentina\n| rowspan=\"5\" |Estadio GEBA\n|-\n|May 4, 2014\n|-\n|May 9, 2014\n|-\n|May 10, 2014\n|-\n|May 11, 2014\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |North America<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.staplescenter.com/news/detail/formula-vol-2-tour-comes-to-los-angeles|title=Formula Vol. 2 Tour comes to Los Angeles {{!}} STAPLES Center|last=Center|first=STAPLES|website=www.staplescenter.com|language=en|access-date=2019-05-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.corrientelatina.com/news/romeo-santos-announces-second-u-s-arena-leg-record-setting-formula-vol-2-tour/|title=Romeo Santos Announces A Second U.S. Arena Leg Of His Record-Setting Formula Vol. 2 Tour|date=2015-01-22|website=CorrienteLatina|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-04}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 21, 2014\n|San Diego\n| rowspan=\"22\" |United States\n|Valley View Casino Center\n|-\n|May 22, 2014\n|Los Angeles\n|Staples Center\n|-\n|May 23, 2014\n|Oakland\n|Oracle Arena\n|-\n|May 25, 2014\n|Las Vegas\n|Mandalay Bay Events Center\n|-\n|May 29, 2014\n|Duluth\n|Infinite Energy Arena\n|-\n|May 30, 2014\n|Orlando\n|Anway Center\n|-\n|May 31, 2014\n|Miami\n|American Airlines Arena\n|-\n|June 4, 2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Houston\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Toyota Center\n|-\n|June 5, 2014\n|-\n|June 6, 2014\n|San Antonio\n|AT&T Center\n|-\n|June 7, 2014\n|Dallas\n|American Airlines Center\n|-\n|June 11, 2014\n|Fairfax\n|EagleBank Arena\n|-\n|June 13, 2014\n|Rosemont\n|Allstate Arena\n|-\n|June 15, 2014\n|Philadelphia\n|Liacouras Center\n|-\n|June 20, 2014\n| r